ÆIn Loving Memory
of
Tom O'Hare
21st Jan. 1934 - 28th Oct. 2008

Take a seat, rest a while, reminisce, chuckle & smile
"Bernadette" Daughter, Sister, Aunty, Wife,
has left too soon from this life.
Don't be sad, just be glad.
She now shares heaven with our Dad
3rd July 1966 - 28th January 2019"≤
ØIN LOVING MEMORY
ALLAN ASHFIELD

A MUCH LOVED DAD, HUSBAND AND FRIEND TO
US ALL, SADLY MISSED
He walked his dog Bazil, and loved to come fishing here.
"TIGHT LINES MATE""ª
∏Janina Koniuszewska

In loving memory
of our dear mum.
Sadly missed.
always remembered.

Passed away July 1996

I sit and wait just lonely me,
Beneath the branches of your tree,
The sun shines warm,
A gentle breeze carries the sweet
fragrance of flowers in the air,
A leaf falls and tangles in my hair.
I'm feeling melancholy, I sigh,
As tear drops quickly fill my eyes,
Suddenly you flutter by,
Oh my beautiful butterfly."ø
